@group DescribeJobs
@endpoint POST /DescribeJobs
@desc Returns a list of Jobs. Use the JobsID and fromDate and toData filters to limit which jobs are returned. The response is sorted by creationDataTime - latest date first. Jobs are normally created by the StartTest, StartCutover, and TerminateTargetInstances APIs. Jobs are also created by DiagnosticLaunch and TerminateDiagnosticInstances, which are APIs available only to *Support* and only used in response to relevant support tickets.
@optional {accountID: str, filters: DescribeJobsRequestFilters, maxResults: int, nextToken: str}
@returns(200) {items: [Job]?, nextToken: str?}

@endgroup

